\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af37 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid539649 Chem 16 June 4 2012\line Urinalysis June 4 2012\line Liver Panel \endash  July and August\line Multiple tests on stool (Briggs) \endash  August 2011\line Upper Endoscopy \endash  August 2011\line 
