\rtlch\fcs1 \af37 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid539649 Over the previous decade and a half, the blood supply to my intestines had changed such that most of the arterial flow bypassed the gut and most of the flow through that area was actually veinous.\~
 Thus, the nutrients and sugars first would go through my heart and then to the rest of my body.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af37 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976062 
